INSERT INTO `wpbj_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2017-05-15 08:50:38','2017-05-15 08:50:38','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!','Hello world!','','trash','open','open','','hello-world__trashed','','','2017-05-24 22:13:29','2017-05-24 22:13:29','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?p=1',0,'post','',5),(2,1,'2017-05-15 08:50:38','2017-05-15 08:50:38','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','trash','closed','open','','sample-page__trashed','','','2017-05-15 21:50:14','2017-05-15 21:50:14','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','','Espresso','','inherit','open','closed','','espresso','','','2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/espresso.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','','Sandwich','','inherit','open','closed','','sandwich','','','2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sandwich.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(6,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','','Coffee','','inherit','open','closed','','coffee','','','2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/coffee.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(7,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','Welcome to your site! This is your homepage, which is what most visitors will see when they come to your site for the first time.','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(8,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:01','2017-05-15 08:58:01','De Amerikaanse jeugdvrienden Ben Cohen en Jerry Greenfield ontmoetten elkaar op High School tijdens de gymles. Ze deelden een liefde voor lekker eten. Na High School gingen ze ieder een eigen weg. In 1978 ontmoetten ze elkaar weer en besloten om samen een ijsbedrijf te beginnen. Met een simpele cursus ijsbereiding als basis begonnen ze met een startkapitaal van $ 12.000 (waarvan $ 4000 vreemd vermogen) hun eigen ijswinkel in een gerenoveerd benzinestation in Vermont.\r\n\r\nToen de vraag naar hun ijs groter werd besloten de oprichters aandelen van hun bedrijf via de beurs te verhandelen. Sinds 1996 is Ben &amp; Jerry’s ook in Nederland verkrijgbaar. In augustus 2000 werd het bedrijf verkocht aan de Nederlandse multinational Unilever en Ben &amp; Jerry\'s wordt inmiddels ook in Nederland geproduceerd.\r\n\r\nHet ijs wordt verkocht in speciale \'scoopshops\' en voorverpakt bij supermarkten, videotheken, benzinestations en bioscopen. Alle smaken zijn verkrijgbaar in een 500ml verpakking (pints) en een beperkt aantal in een kleinere 150ml verpakking. De 150ml versie is voorzien van een houten lepeltje dat in het deksel is geplaatst.','Over Ons','','publish','closed','closed','','overons','','','2017-05-23 18:30:45','2017-05-23 18:30:45','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:02','2017-05-15 08:58:02','<strong>Heb je een vraag over...? Hulp nodig met...? Wil je iets kwijt over….? Wil je weten wie, wat, waar, waarom of wanneer….? </strong>\r\n\r\nWe vinden het leuk om van je te horen. Alle tips, vragen of eventueel klachten zijn altijd welkom. We horen graag van jou dus laat gerust iets weten.\r\nGeef ons je mening over de site of stel ons een vraag.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>0032 (0)78/152201 (verlaagd tarief)</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>Ben &amp; Jerry\'s Belgieë, </em>\r\n<em>Humaniteitslaan 292,</em>\r\n<em>1190 Vorst, Belgiëe</em></p>','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2017-05-23 18:39:56','2017-05-23 18:39:56','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:02','2017-05-15 08:58:02','','What\'s New','','publish','open','closed','','whatsnew','','','2017-05-22 05:47:10','2017-05-22 05:47:10','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:02','2017-05-15 08:58:02','This is an example of a homepage section. Homepage sections can be any page other than the homepage itself, including the page that shows your latest blog posts.','A homepage section','','trash','closed','closed','','a-homepage-section__trashed','','','2017-05-15 21:50:27','2017-05-15 21:50:27','',0,'http://localhost/CMP/CMP2/BenJerry/WP_BJ/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(12,1,'2017-05-15 08:58:00','2017-05-15 08:58:00','{\n    \"widget_text[2]\": {\n        \"starter_content\": true,\n        \"value\": {\n            \"encoded_serialized_instance\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"Find Us\",\n            \"is_widget_customizer_js_value\": true,\n            \"instance_hash_key\": \"517cdb77407599f2198030eb889dcdb0\"\n        },\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n 